                    <h1 style="font-family:serif; font-size: 45px;">What is Microgram ?</h1>
                    <br>
                    <p style="font-family:sans-serif; font-style:italic; font-size: 26px;" >Microstructures are an integral member in the world of material sciences. Microstructure design and manipulation is the basis of much of materials research. However most of the microstructure data collected in research rarely gets shared.</p>
                    <br>
                    <p style="font-family:sans-serif; font-style:italic; font-size: 26px;">Microgram is a platform which enables researchers in materials science to share and collaborate materials research in the realm of microstructures. The platform provides for easy upload, tagging and sharing of microstructure images and allows for complete control over who can access your data.</p>
                </div>
